- [ ] [P2] [chore] `Superset: Show Diagnostics` webview — one-click snapshot of every subsystem (terminals / mDNS / topology / todo / engines / activation session), with Copy-to-clipboard and Save-to-file buttons. Complements the existing `superset.showLogs` (time-series log) with a structured "now" view, unblocks GitHub-issue triage. See [plans/2026-06-24-chore-show-diagnostics-webview.md](plans/2026-06-24-chore-show-diagnostics-webview.md). See scan note 2026-06-24#6A.
- [ ] [P1] [chore] VSIX cross-platform packaging sanity — `.vscodeignore` exclude dev artifacts (test/, src/, scripts/, **/**tests**/**) while intentionally keeping `@homebridge/node-pty-prebuilt-multiarch/prebuilds/` for all target platforms; add `scripts/verify-vsix.sh` that post-checks the .vsix; wire into `npm run build`. See [plans/2026-06-23-chore-vsix-cross-platform-sanity.md](plans/2026-06-23-chore-vsix-cross-platform-sanity.md). See scan note 2026-06-23#5A.
